Journal Story: Ready to be back out on the trail.

I am coming back on this year to hike with Sookie from Minnesota, who is coming back to try for her thru-hike again. I will meet her at mile 309 and hike until I want to come home or finish a second thru-hike, whichever. Looking forward to hiking with Sookie again and possibly Papa Al and Philco on up the trail. Also looking forward to meeting all the new hikers and making new friends.
Not long now. Ten weeks or so to go. It will be here soon but not soon enough.
